## Evidence Collection Schedule

### Daily (Automated)
- Pull {{LOG_SINK}} audit logs
- Review {{ERROR_TRACKER}} error dashboard
- Check {{UPTIME_MONITOR}} status
- Screenshot each for evidence archive

### Weekly (Manual)
- {{AUTH_PROVIDER}}: Export user list, verify membership, remove unused users
- {{LOG_SINK}}: Review data access events filtered by `{{TENANT_ISOLATION_FIELD}}`
- {{ERROR_TRACKER}}: Review new and repeated errors — confirm no PII in stack traces
- Database: Verify all queries include `{{TENANT_ISOLATION_FIELD}}`
- API Security Checklist above — run it

### Monthly (Audit Package)
Collect and store in `/compliance/monthly/YYYY-MM/`:

| System | Evidence |
|--------|---------|
| GitHub | PR approval history |
| {{DEPLOY_PLATFORM}} | Deployment logs |
| {{LOG_SINK}} | Audit log export |
| {{AUTH_PROVIDER}} | Access log screenshots |
| {{BILLING_PROVIDER}} | Billing event log |

